*
 * Controls the navigation bar.
 * Uses the same routes object defined in {@link PageControl}
 *
 * #### SCSS import:
 * ```
 * @import "~@orloxx/ui-core/scss/navigation";
 * ```
 *
 * @example
 * const Nav = withRoute(Navigation);
 *
 * @example
 * <Nav routes={routes} />
